column5: Heading up to the St. lawrence next week for our annual fishing trip, just wondered if anyone had any updates on how the fishing has been.  I have already made my trip to Gander Mountain to by a few new weapons to the tool box!
know nothing about that body of water for i have never been that far north but im sure you will be succesful and have a great report for us when you return good luck and welcome to the board
